snippet.textDisplay:
On behalf of Australia I sincerely apologise to the international community for this disaster. 
Australia has turned into a highly controlled and unwelcoming nation. All sense of logic and good taste has been lost.
This virus has created an unwarranted frenzy in the leaders of our great nation.
Many decisions made have been senseless, pointless and have created a massive blowout in the budget, huge debts at all levels of government and created an embarrassment on an international level. Today we see our national being almost fully vaccinated and cases going through the roof. It was all for nothing, as I assumed was going to be the case. For this reason I never undertook any tests, never waited hours in any lines and have not been vaccinated. I knew this was unnecessary and a waste of my time, government money and resources. Two years later I am just fine, as expected.
I am sorry for the embarrassment that the Australian Government has caused our nation and the unnecessary pain and suffering it has cause our most gullible of citizens.

I am sorry for the embarrassment that the Australian Government has caused our nation and the unnecessary pain and suffering it has cause our most gullible of citizens.
